  "title": "HR INTERNS (No experience required as Daily Training will be provided) #NJH",
  "description": "<p>We are hiring due to our internal business expansion.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are seeking high energy, dynamic, self-starter and high-self-development individuals to join us!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Minimum 3 months commitment, and the roles can be extended up to 12 months!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Job scope:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>To Engage in candidate sourcing activities, such as publishing job advertisements and conducting candidate referrals, to ensure a consistent supply of candidates to meet internal stakeholders' needs.</li>\n  <li>To Manage candidates job expectations, their payroll and employment benefits.</li>\n  <li>Involve in onboarding and offboarding of contractors when required</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>A Levels, Diploma or Degree in any discipline</li>\n  <li>Possess enthusiasm, passion for people, high initiative &amp; team playing</li>\n  <li>Active participation in sports or school activities is an added advantage</li>\n  <li>No Experience required as DAILY Training will be provided</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interest applicants, pls email updated resume to <a href=\"mailto:jessie@recruitexpress.com.sg\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">jessie@recruitexpress.com.sg</a></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Jessie Hoe Huey Miin</p>\n<p>CEI R1103861</p>\n<p>EA: 99C4599</p>",
